ADDITIONAL ATTRIBUTIONS:

This project incorporates concepts and inspiration from various classic games
and open-source projects. See CREDITS.md for detailed attribution.

Game Concepts:
- Snake: Based on classic Nokia game (public domain)
- Tetris: Based on Alexey Pajitnov's original (game mechanics in public domain)
- Flappy Bird: Inspired by Dong Nguyen's game (mechanic inspiration)
- Breakout: Based on Atari classic (public domain)
- Space Wars: Inspired by classic arcade shooters and open-source implementations
- Pong: Based on Atari classic (public domain)
- Dodge: Original creation for this project

Libraries Used:
- M5StickCPlus2 Library: MIT License
- Arduino Framework: LGPL 2.1
- PlatformIO: Apache 2.0

All original code created for this project is released under the MIT License
above. Referenced libraries and inspirations retain their original licenses.
